## *Зависимости:*

1. FTXUI (auto install)
2. pkg-config
3. libpqxx-dev
4. libsqlite3-dev
5. SQLiteCpp

```bash
# Зависимости компиляции
sudo apt update
sudo apt install build-essential cmake pkg-config

# libpqxx и SQLite
sudo apt install libpqxx-dev libsqlite3-dev

git clone https://github.com/SRombauts/SQLiteCpp.git
cd SQLiteCpp
mkdir build && cd build
cmake .. -DSQLITECPP_BUILD_TESTS=OFF -DSQLITECPP_BUILD_EXAMPLES=OFF
make
sudo make install
```
